Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 真不可思議 為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:12.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}你一笑起來 心裡總會閃亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:15.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:18.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:30.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回過神來 發現已經著迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:36.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}"這種事會有的吧?" 你這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:41.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}緊緊地握住我的手 體溫傳達給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:46.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}不管去哪裡 都感覺無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:52.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:58.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景畫一樣 展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:03.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 無論天空有多寬闊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:09.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:14.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑聲迴響在耳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:22.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充滿溫柔、愉悅的感覺 還有新的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:28.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一步 一步 前進吧
